{
  "stem": "1857.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I was getting closer to a certain point, I saw masses of people yelling, 'Kill the Jews!",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beat the Jews!' And this was right around a building that was, before the war, building for Jewish students who lived outside of Krakow, but were-- but were studying in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after the war, it was a building for Jewish refugees, housing Jewish refugees from the east.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I started running home, because my parents were home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as soon as I came home, my father and my mother, and my father's friend who came for Saturday dinner-- dinnertime was noontime-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were pale, because they heard people running down the street. 'Kill the Jews!",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Beat the Jews!'",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walked over, and I closed the window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About two minutes later, somebody's knocking on the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And four policemen and a civilian walk into the apartment and says, 'Who was shooting out of the window?' It was a pretext.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, 'We don't have a gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody was shooting.'",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Search.' But they didn't really search.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, 'Take them out.' And they took us out on the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And right away, hundreds of Poles-- 'Kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Beat the Jews.' And I was  sure that they're going to lynch us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that moment, a detachment of Polish police was going to make order.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And an officer was on a horse in front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a schoolmate of mine became a high officer of police after the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I started yelling that I am a friend of [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Adam ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Kuchil ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Please do something for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
